        "description": "The sequel to the popular Cueist pool/snooker game, Cueist 2 brings unparalelled realism to online VR cue sports. This is not a casual point and click type game, but a deeper simulation which will reward real skill.\n\n - Play online against your friends with voice chat and Meta Avatars or get some practice in versus the CPU players.\n - Use a natural cueing action using the Touch Controllers, or attach a real cue for the ultimate in feel and accuracy.\n - A choice of specialist cues enables various spin, swerve, masse, and jump shots.\n - Choose between 9 Ball, 8 Ball, UK 8 Ball, and Snooker.\n\nThe latest update adds:\n - Click the left thumbstick to switch between smooth movement and stepped movement (for those who might find smooth movement unsettling)\n - Click the right thumbstick to switch between smooth rotation and snap turns.\n - A new laser aim pointer to aid lining up shots\n - When the shot is lined up, you can nowhold the Y button on the left controller to enable Autoplay",
